nl.esciencecenter.octopus.adaptors.gridengine

Class GridEngineCredentials

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.esciencecenter.octopus.adaptors.gridengine.GridEngineCredentials
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Credentials

    public class GridEngineCredentials
extends Object
implements Credentials
    GridEngine credentials implementation. As GridEngine uses ssh for interacting with the scheduler, actually creates ssh credentials by forwarding the request to the engine again, after replacing the scheme.
    Author:
    Niels Drost
